{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>TechnoSorcery</strong> is a rhythm-lite spellcasting arcade game that takes you on a narrative driven adventure.  Instead of focusing on precise input timings like other rhythm games, <strong>TechnoSorcery</strong> challenges the player to learn a variety short input sequences (spells) that are aligned to the beat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/Gameplay.gif?t=1733454633\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Rhythm-Based Spellcasting</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feel like a true Sorcerer as you gain mastery of the 8 elemental notes and memorize over 100 unique spells.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/Spellbook.gif?t=1733454633\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Narrative Driven Adventure</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join <strong>Aiden</strong> and his spirit companion <strong>Silven</strong> as they travel the world learning Sorcery on an impossible quest.  Play over 40 story levels as you discover the truth behind Aiden's spellcasting abilities, despite him being Mute.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/Dialog.gif?t=1733454633\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customize your Deck and prepare for Battle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock challenging Boss Battles as you progress through the story.  This fast-paced Card-Battling mode builds upon the skills you gain during the story and pushes them to the limit.  Every spell now has a unique ability - summon powerful creatures, deal direct damage, give yourself buffs, or just even fill your opponent's deck with Toxic Shrooms.  The choice is yours when you build a deck of your own.  But be quick; your opponent will be casting back with a unique deck of their own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/BattleMode.gif?t=1733454633\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">User Generated Content</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Still looking for an additional challenge? Create, Upload, and Play levels of your own in the fully functional Level Editor.  Or just download and play levels created by other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/LevelEditor.gif?t=1733454633\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733454633","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/page.bg.jpg?t=1733454633","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/117978f126f1a76c68489efd11aa472de342a74b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733454633","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/117978f126f1a76c68489efd11aa472de342a74b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733454633","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":30},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>TechnoSorcery</strong> is a rhythm-lite spellcasting arcade game that takes you on a narrative driven adventure.  Instead of focusing on precise input timings like other rhythm games, <strong>TechnoSorcery</strong> challe